  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chunky chips</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619780849109-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619780849109-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619780849109-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619780849109-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619780849109-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 6-8 min or until part-cooked</p><p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong> to a large bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cider vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Set aside until serving – this is your <strong>pickled red cabbage</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1619780854979-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1619780854979-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1619780854979-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
